																		Thanks, Attribution, and Other Matters
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mrwrong" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2039383); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2039383&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610182408" alt="MrWrong" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2039383)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mrwrong" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2039383); return false;" >MrWrong</a></span> <span class="odate time_1434510913 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">17 Jun 2015 03:15</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2318728">
									

<p>Firstly, I would to thank people who have looked through it such as Cimmerian, Wogglebug, Pheonix24 among others.</p>
<p>SCPs mentioned in this article are:</p>
<ul>
<li>SCP-173 (The Sculpture) by Moto42</li>
<li>SCP-2317 (A Door to Another World) by DrClef</li>
</ul>
<p>Stylistics for the iPhone-esque portion is unceremoniously adapted from (after some fiddling with the code to suit my purposes) LurkD's format of the AIAD series.</p>
<p>Naming scheme for universes are derived from Experiment Log T-98816-OC108/682, particularly the portion on SCP-507.</p>
<p>And WTH is happening here?</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;show&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>The <em>true</em> Foundation in this story operates on the multiversal scale and props up branches in various realities a la <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scantron-s-proposal">Scantron's proposal</a>. SCPs are moved about across realities to extend time to study on them, and entire realities can be reduced to test sites. For instance, 2317 was unleashed just to observe it in the &quot;wild&quot;.</p>
<p>And the &quot;true&quot; Foundation operates at the base of the multiverse, as a literal foundation of all reality.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>Overall, this is 1/3 lampshading those &quot;tales featuring 173 and the SCP format&quot;, 1/3 &quot;why does 173's description begin with &quot;Moved to Site-19&#8230;&quot; and 1/3 the potential start to a series/canon?</p>

							</div>

								
